{"tha-ap223:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap223:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap223:0.3":"1 Alambanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap223:1.1":"“Atthadassissa bhagavato, ","tha-ap223:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap223:1.3":"Alambanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap223:1.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap223:2.1":"Dharanim patipajjami, ","tha-ap223:2.2":"vipulam sagarapparam; ","tha-ap223:2.3":"Panesu ca issariyam, ","tha-ap223:2.4":"vattemi vasudhaya ca. ","tha-ap223:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap223:3.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap223:3.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap223:3.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap223:4.1":"Ito dvesatthikappamhi, ","tha-ap223:4.2":"tayo asimsu khattiya; ","tha-ap223:4.3":"Ekapassitanama te, ","tha-ap223:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap223:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap223:5.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap223:5.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap223:5.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap223:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma alambanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap223:7.1":"Alambanadayakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}